data.description: Welcome to this beautifully UPDATED home in a wonderful location with 3 beds and 3 full baths! The open concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas, perfect for entertaining! The primary bedroom boasts an updated ensuite bathroom. Another 2 spacious bedrooms share a hallway bathroom just updated last month! Oversized 2-car garage. Spacious family room and a third full bath complete the LL. Other updates include brand new kitchen counters, cabinets, back splash, oven/range, dishwasher, kitchen floor, brand new carpet, brand new interior doors except primary bathroom door, fresh interior paint, all windows, sliding door to patio and much more! Please see feature sheet for full list of updates! All windows and patio doors come with a lifetime warranty!
